# Keep the build context small + fast. NOTE: sdk/ is intentionally NOT ignored —
# crates/ledge-rpc/build.rs codegens from sdk/schema/ledge.capnp at build time.
target/
.git/
docs/
formal/
.github/
**/*.md
# NOTE: deploy/ is NOT ignored — the Dockerfile COPYs deploy/docker/entrypoint.sh.
# It is small (yaml + sh), so the context cost is negligible.
